{"tid":1633741,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"點解黨鐵自炒同老解有黃𣄃舉無人講","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:04:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T07:15:54.000Z","uid":165012,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"18cbd8c0e0cd798537716b1bd5bcb91d2d5cdcd5","tid":1633741,"uid":165012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:04:29.000Z","msg":"俾人spin走晒? 明明呢兩單野都係好撚大獲"},{"pid":"f0365a1de11b44217ace66418d6f9e88febdd904","tid":1633741,"uid":165012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:05:01.000Z","msg":"自推1/20"},{"pid":"db10b72be9d4a40dc14782189ffcedfbf955608a","tid":1633741,"uid":167011,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但勇和齊上齊落唔撚得？"},{"pid":"8f8dd0bd540b775cc9542075b701293a89165d2e","tid":1633741,"uid":159762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:05:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港警察濫權實錄資料庫</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4lKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=dda8908e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有英文同日文版 大家落力share俾更多外國人睇！！</span>"},{"pid":"c46291f70921dc9be8ff570e5b3532aa72704dfd","tid":1633741,"uid":165012,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:07:51.000